parameters: Audience: Lord Cerberus Octopus-! Look this way---!!

Memimi: Hehe... Today's Monster Fight is a huge success too.
The Monster Fight, which used to be a dark society's betting
match, has been transformed into a costumed pro-wrestling
organization by the volunteers of the monsters, thanks to
Bunny-chan's proposal...

Cerberus Octopus: Mos mos mos... Here I go~, Mosman Body
Press!!

Cerberus Octopus: Take this, Octopus Chop!! For the fight
money and the fans, I can't afford to lose!!

Memimi: Those two are now the top stars of Monster Fight,
competing for the first and second place. Ever since we
opened the matches to the public, their popularity with
women has been incredible, attracting fans from outside the
prefecture...

Bunny-chan: The match is over... Memimi-chan, you came to
see us! It was a huge success today too, with amazing
viewership for the live stream The merchandise sales are
also doing well

Memimi: It's all thanks to Bunny-chan working hard as the
head of operations and referee! Monster Fight has completely
become a new specialty of Dorieto City. Now, Dorieto City,
which was lacking in industries, will flourish with tourism
and merchandise sales...
